<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lei gimum thihna gam ahin,
 Zion khawvak ngaktute;
 Muong taka ana ipmute,
 Lalpa tuokdi'n kaitho un,

[V2]
 Ni lopi tak hungtung ding chu,
 Kawlni suok bangin I Lalpau hungvak intin;
 A Aw zate than apat hungtho ding,
 Van leh meipi kalah,
 Khensate tawh I Lalpau tuok dingin va leng hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Lungkhama kapte hai tau in,
 Hun sawttak ngak talo ding;
 Lungkham mauna'n van a thawng hi,
 Lalpa ngai buoita kiu in.

[V4]
 3. I Lalpa thutiem bangzel in,
 Hun a lamdang thil a thak;
 Lunggil buokna'dim suthieng un,
 Thagau thiengtho samlut un.

[V5]
 4. Lei leh vana thil cheng sangin,
 Muh ka nuom ie ka Tanpa,
 Keidi'n Saron pak bang na lun-
 Ni chuh hungtun sak ta uo.</lyrics>
<title>Zion Khawvak Ngakte</title>
<hymn_number>226</hymn_number>
<author>Pautinkhup</author>
</song>